creator: FlyBird Casual Games
descriptionHtml:
Grand Hospital is a hospital simulation game that truly restores the operation and construction of a hospital! Here you need to run a personalized hospital, recruit skilled staff, and use professional and fast treatment techniques and equipment to cure patients with various difficult diseases. Let's train more great doctors who have good skills and are committed to saving lives. Come and build an elite team!

Game Features.
- You'll get a realistic and rich experience of running a hospital simulation!
Design and decorate the hospital, rationally arrange the layout of various departments and equipment according to your preferences. There are triage desks for diagnosing illnesses, treatment rooms and laboratories for healing. Many different styles of hospitals are waiting for you to unlock!

‒ Recruit powerful professional doctors and nurses!
Recruit professional doctors and nurses from different departments. Do a good job in time and task management to form a professional team. Speed up doctors' treatment and improve the hospital's visibility!

‒ Receive all kinds of patients, discover the cause, and heal patients!
The image of the patient and the cause of the disease are derived from daily life, making the character more vivid and imaginative, so that the player has a greater sense of immersion.

- Keep making money and saving money!
Recruiting excellent teams, improving skills, building various cutting-edge medical equipment, and treating patients, so that you will continue to make money and develop into a wealthy Grand Hospital!

‒ Comparing competitions can inspire players to have a stronger desire to win!
Take part in tournaments and ranking matches. Challenge various difficult tasks and jobs to create a super hospital with a higher cure rate!

Break through the thinking and constraints of traditional simulation games to give players a free and open creative world. Join the hospital as soon as possible and experience the successful life as the president of Grand Hospital!
descriptionShort: Play clinic game, build your own super hospital! Create the doctor story!
